Welcome back to The Best & The Brightest. I=E2=80=99m Abby
Livingston.

=C2=A0

As Washington contemplates an emerging constitutional clash between the Whi=
te House and the courts, I=E2=80=99m grateful to share my partner John Heil=
emann=E2=80=99s engrossing interview with Harvard Law professor Laurence Tr=
ibe. As John notes, Tribe is a 36-time litigator before the Supreme
Court, and has served as a legal tutor to a staggering number of political =
and judicial eminences across the ideological spectrum. So when he speaks o=
