ect 2025 and occasional statements about how he would terminate the Constit=
ution if necessary. In a sense, you could say we got what we asked for. But=
 it doesn=E2=80=99t mean that it=E2=80=99s not a radical, revolutionary scr=
apping of the whole system. Talk about impeachable offenses=E2=80=94virtual=
ly everything that has happened since he was inaugurated the second time is=
 an impeachable
